serves: 100
---
- 10kg fusilli pasta
- 2 kg pickles
- 1 kg White onions
- 4 kg Sweet peppers
- 4 kg Tomatoes
- 1 litre Olive oil
- 250 ml vinegar
- 150 g Mustard Salt
- 25 teaspoon salt
- 12 teaspoon pepper
---
Cook the pasta. al dente please.
Cut the other ingredients into small pieces. 
Make a mustard sauce: add the vinegar to the mustard then the olive oil like for a mayonnaise. 
Mix everything when the pasta is cold.